Enter an SQL query

SELECT author, title, amount
FROM book 
WHERE amount IN (SELECT amount
                FROM book
                GROUP BY amount
HAVING COUNT(amount) = 1 );

Query result:
+---------------+-----------------------+--------+
| author        | title                 | amount |
+---------------+-----------------------+--------+
| Булгаков М.А. | Белая гвардия         | 5      |
| Есенин С.А.   | Стихотворения и поэмы | 15     |
+---------------+-----------------------+--------+


