Enter an SQL query

DELETE FROM supply 
WHERE author IN(
     SELECT author
     FROM book
     GROUP BY author
     HAVING SUM(amount) > 10
     );
SELECT * FROM supply;

Query result:
+-----------+---------------+----------------+--------+--------+
| supply_id | title         | author         | price  | amount |
+-----------+---------------+----------------+--------+--------+
| 1         | Лирика        | Пастернак Б.Л. | 518.99 | 2      |
| 3         | Белая гвардия | Булгаков М.А.  | 540.50 | 7      |
+-----------+---------------+----------------+--------+--------+


